line`\n+\n+To force single line where layout\n+\n+- **Default value**: `false`\n+- **Possible values**: `true`, `false`\n+\n+#### `false` (default):\n+\n+```rust\n+impl<T> Lorem for T\n+where\n+    Option<T>: Ipsum,\n+{\n+    ...\n+}\n+```\n+\n+#### `true`:\n+\n+```rust\n+impl<T> Lorem for T where\n+    Option<T>: Ipsum {\n+    ...\n+}\n+```\n+\n+See also [`brace_style`](#brace_style), [`control_brace_style`](#control_brace_style).\n+\n+\n ## `force_explicit_abi`\n \n Always print the abi for extern items"}]}